      <title>丰业银行表示，应对加息的房主削减了支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-28/homeowners-coping-with-rate-hikes-cut-spending-scotiabank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据新斯科舍银行称，加拿大浮动利率抵押贷款房主的支出削减幅度是固定利率贷款借款人的两倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-28/homeowners-coping-with-rate-hikes-cut-spending-scotiabank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 16:42:12 GMT</pubDate>
